    public class DisposablePirateFleetManager
extends DisposableFleetManager
    Adds the following types of fleets: 1) Weak pirates to any nearby populated system, sometimes. 2) Pirates to systems with markets with Pirate Activity; number/strength depends on base level 3) Systems with a bounty; number/strength depends on size of markets.
    Author:
    Alex Mosolov Copyright 2018 Fractal Softworks, LLC
